<HEADLINE>
<P>
BRIEFLY 
</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Cineplex to Repurchase Screens: Cineplex Odeon announced that it would 
repurchase 153 motion picture screens in Canada for $47 million ($55.25 million 
Canadian) from affiliates of Carena Developments Ltd., which had purchased the 
theaters a year ago. When the earlier transaction took place, Cineplex netted 
about $51.4 million (Canadian) after paying certain fees. Cineplex -- itself on 
the auction block -- said it was repurchasing the theaters because of renewed 
box office strength in Canada. 
</P>
