</P>
</HEADLINE>
<TEXT>
<P>
Former super-welterweight boxing champion Lupe Aquino, 26, pleaded no contest 
to vehicular manslaughter charges in Superior Court in Santa Monica, for 
killing two passengers in his car in a drunk-driving accident last year. 
</P>
</TEXT>
<TYPE>
<P>
